            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is regarding Ruh Continuum K-12 School, Singanallur. Tried reaching the school to get an introduction and fee structure as we are relocating from Malaysia to India but the admission team bluntly asked us to pay the application fee( no introduction nothing) for our two children and then the entrance will be conducted; post which only the management will let the parents know about the fees and introduction of the school. To enroll the children we just don't need their website or the word \"Reputed\" from their management but they need to be friendly enough to guide the parent approaching asking for details. With this attitude of management and staff \" not sure what is the word reputation means to them may be just another business\" Glad we got to know you even before enrolling our children.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
