          "reviewBody": "BEST SCHOOL IN TAMIL NADU!! This school looks like a world-class AND has world-class teaching facilities. The classrooms have digital, white and chalk boards, separate reading corners, placements for books, device racks, discussion tables and more! The teachers there will help your child be the best they can. The school offers Cambridge and IB curriculums, which have technology-based lessons (but there is still traditional writing work). One important subject is Leader In Me which is a program that helps your child become a leader.  Hope this review helps you!",
